data.eml:eml: Phrudoneura (Diptera: Dolichopodidae) from Australia and Melanesia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal volume Bickel, Daniel J. (2013): Phrudoneura (Diptera: Dolichopodidae) from Australia and Melanesia. Zootaxa 3680 (1), DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3680.1.4
